model.name: Waterfront Mule
model.disambiguatingDescription: The Waterfront mule is revisited this season with its front strap embossed with Louis Vuitton's iconic Monogram pattern, creating a puffer effect. This pool slide, made of waterproof rubber, also features a comfortable anatomic insole embossed with the LV Initials. The lightweight, flexible outsole is debossed with the Louis Vuitton signature.
